				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Thu%E1%BA%A5n-D%C3%A2n/%C4%90%E1%BA%A3-m%E1%BA%A1ch/poem-geKt6Swor5lXWclTfF3dzg">Đả mạch - 打麥</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Thu%E1%BA%A5n-D%C3%A2n/author-1-ewUEdMXYGTpOMxwIc6Ig">Trương Thuấn Dân</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Di%C3%AAu-N%C3%A3i/Ho%C3%A0ng-H%C3%A0-kh%C3%BAc/poem-gYokr6y0qHZ7KA6q1dxEWw">Hoàng Hà khúc - 黃河曲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Di%C3%AAu-N%C3%A3i/author-Fd7oZerPVEVOXx_JIj1fmg">Diêu Nãi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Mao-%C4%91%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-ki%E1%BB%83m-hi%E1%BB%87u-thu-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1o-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-1Qx5AmoG4ccNeGZcWFetDw">Mao đường kiểm hiệu thu đạo kỳ 2 - 茅堂檢校收稻其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Li%E1%BB%85u-T%C3%B4ng-Nguy%C3%AAn/Nam-gi%E1%BA%A3n-trung-%C4%91%E1%BB%81/poem-GPPhFlDbIe5Qbvv-eeKJog">Nam giản trung đề - 南澗中題</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Li%E1%BB%85u-T%C3%B4ng-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-cFCa0wn9ZwJZJ5nwtlsQmQ">Liễu Tông Nguyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-B%E1%BB%89nh-Khi%C3%AAm/Ng%E1%BB%A5-h%E1%BB%A9ng-ph%C3%A0m-t%E1%BB%A9-th%E1%BB%A7-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-3NiSwKa-d7KHvXhS2ibMmw">Ngụ hứng phàm tứ thủ kỳ 2 - 寓興凡四首其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-B%E1%BB%89nh-Khi%C3%AAm/author-Rv6locqJPIunovJpeqDNxA">Nguyễn Bỉnh Khiêm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Nguy%C3%AAn/Quy-thanh-ch%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng/poem-C2ZBwxUwABcFxmGaoHj-MA">Quy thanh chướng - 歸青嶂</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-dGtRDyQcsXmBKCUpPVl6Mw">Phan Trường Nguyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Di%C3%AAu-Nguy%E1%BB%87t-Hoa/S%E1%BB%9F-phi-o%C3%A1n/poem-NZE_65kJDjT-Q2yTth3xkw">Sở phi oán - 楚妃怨</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Di%C3%AAu-Nguy%E1%BB%87t-Hoa/author--szLFQhJ5G33TIr-G4r5nw">Diêu Nguyệt Hoa</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Nguy%C3%AAn-H%C3%A0nh/Th%C3%ADnh-ca/poem-Jd85ySg6a-e4ZqBpCocV-w">Thính ca - 聽歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Nguy%C3%AAn-H%C3%A0nh/author-xb9f8XgZhtsCrJqig5eRWg">Vũ Nguyên Hành</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-H%E1%BB%AFu-Tr%C3%A1c/Th%E1%BB%A7-37/poem-msHdhAxKvjbzuvxiNLzIwA">Thủ 37 - 首３７</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-H%E1%BB%AFu-Tr%C3%A1c/author-17RN7O2NKv8SmVJdOlpdFg">Lê Hữu Trác</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/V%C3%B5ng-Xuy%C3%AAn-nh%C3%A0n-c%C6%B0-t%E1%BA%B7ng-B%C3%B9i-t%C3%BA-t%C3%A0i-%C4%90%E1%BB%8Bch/poem-y9gZometdRFUsWlAUMEwMg">Võng Xuyên nhàn cư tặng Bùi tú tài Địch - 輞川閑居贈裴秀才迪</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/author-9f1Hth0gmM_PXzGNXg5Fog">Vương Duy</a>)<br></div>	</div>
